# {{name}}

AI tool config repo, managed by [claudesync](https://github.com/DuchitskyDA/claudesync).

## Install on a new machine

1. Install [claudesync](https://github.com/DuchitskyDA/claudesync/releases)
2. Open it and configure:
   - Repo URL: `https://github.com/{{owner}}/{{name}}`
   - Rules target: `~/.claude` (auto-detected)
3. Click **Pull & Install**

Or manually:

```bash
git clone https://github.com/{{owner}}/{{name}}.git ~/Documents/{{name}}
cd ~/Documents/{{name}}
RULES_TARGET=~/.claude ./install.sh    # macOS / Linux
# Windows: powershell -ExecutionPolicy Bypass -File .\install.ps1
```

